properties.areaDesc: Death Valley National Park; Western Mojave Desert
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 9 at 3:50AM PST until February 10 at 3:00AM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Death Valley National Park and Western Mojave Desert.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 3 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult for motorcycles...large trucks...trailers
and campers especially on east-west oriented sections of roads.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 3 AM PST MONDAY
